<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email - Monobase</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <div style="background-color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        
        <!-- Header -->
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">Welcome to Monobase!</h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <p style="color: #34495e; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Hello {{name}},
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #34495e; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Thank you for joining Monobase Platform! To complete your registration and secure your account, please verify your email address by clicking the button below.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
            <a href="{{verificationLink}}" 
               style="background-color: #3498db; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3);">
                Verify Your Email Address
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Alternative Link -->
        <div style="margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #ecf0f1; border-radius: 5px;">
            <p style="color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
            </p>
            <p style="color: #3498db; font-size: 14px; margin: 10px 0 0 0; word-break: break-all;">
                {{verificationLink}}
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Security Notice -->
        <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
            <p style="color: #34495e; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <strong>Why verify your email?</strong>
            </p>
            <ul style="color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 14px; margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Secure your account and protect your information</li>
                <li>Receive important notifications about your appointments</li>
                <li>Get updates about your orders and results</li>
                <li>Enable password recovery if needed</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div style="margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;">
            <p style="color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
                If you didn't create an account with Monobase, you can safely ignore this email.
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 12px; margin: 20px 0 0 0; text-align: center;">
                This email was sent to <strong>{{email}}</strong><br>
                Â© 2024 Monobase Platform. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>